' Linear Modus Ponens — end-to-end: a σ ⊸ τ transformer is registered in the
' capability registry; the deployer presents witness σ into the linear zone; the
' capability CONSUMES σ exactly once (no double-spend) and PRODUCES τ; the cost is
' conserved (req(σ⊸τ) = req(σ)+req(τ)). Channel-level lemma:
' lolly_modus_ponens_channel_decomposition; reduction lives in RhoReduction.v.
'
' Source of truth for Figure 5 in docs/theory/cost-accounting-linear-logic.md.
' Palette:  Deployer=salmon #F8C3B8 · registry=indigo #C5CAE9 · Δ-zone=orange #FFCC80
'           capability=amber #FFECB3
'   arrows: setup/control/ack=blue #1565C0 · witness flow (present/produce/yield)=green #2E7D32
'           consume/spend=red #C62828
'   notes:  Δ-gains=green #C8E6C9 · Δ-spent=red #EF9A9A · conservation=amber #FFF8E1
' Render:  plantuml -tsvg docs/theory/diagrams/lolly-modus-ponens-sequence.puml

@startuml lolly-modus-ponens-sequence
!theme plain
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor             #444444
  LifeLineBorderColor    #666666
  ParticipantBorderColor #333333
  NoteBorderColor        #666666
}
skinparam defaultFontName "sans-serif"
title Linear modus ponens:  σ ⊗ (σ ⊸ τ) ⊢ τ
autonumber

actor       "Deployer"                          as D     #F8C3B8
participant "rho:system:capabilities\nregistry"  as REG   #C5CAE9
participant "Linear zone Δ\n(witness store)"     as DELTA #FFCC80
participant "Capability\nσ ⊸ τ"                  as CAP   #FFECB3

D   -[#1565C0]>  REG : register transformer σ ⊸ τ
REG -[#1565C0]>  CAP : install capability
REG -[#1565C0]-> D   : capability handle

D   -[#2E7D32]>  DELTA : present witness σ
note right of DELTA #C8E6C9 : Δ = [σ];  cost req(σ) accounted
D   -[#1565C0]>  CAP : invoke σ ⊸ τ  with σ
CAP -[#C62828]>  DELTA : consume σ  (consume_linear_atom)
note right of DELTA #EF9A9A
  Δ = [ ] — σ spent exactly once;
  a 2nd consume of σ would return None
end note
DELTA -[#1565C0]-> CAP : Some [ ]
CAP -[#2E7D32]>  DELTA : produce τ
note right of DELTA #C8E6C9 : Δ = [τ]
CAP -[#2E7D32]-> D : yield τ

note over D, CAP #FFF8E1
  <b>ll_lolly_resource_flow_conservative</b>
  req(σ ⊸ τ) = req(σ) + req(τ)   — no resource created ex nihilo
end note
@enduml
